---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Curricula Standards" description="RACP Basic Training curricula standards — competencies, EPAs, and knowledge guides.">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Curricula Standards</h1>
    <p>The three pillars that define what trainees must be, do, and know.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>
      The RACP curriculum model is made up of curricula standards supported by learning, teaching, and assessment programs.
    </p>
    <ul class="item-list">
      <li><strong>Learning & teaching programs</strong> — strategies and methods, including required and recommended learning activities</li>
      <li><strong>Assessment programs</strong> — planned use of assessment methods to picture trainee competence over time</li>
      <li><strong>Curricula standards</strong> — educational objectives and the standard against which trainees are measured</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Be — Competencies</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">49 competencies across 10 domains of professional practice</div>
      <p>Outlines expected professional behaviours, values, and practices of trainees.</p>
    </div>
    <h3>Domains include</h3>
    <ul class="item-list">
      <li>Communication</li>
      <li>Cultural competence</li>
      <li>Ethics and professional behaviour</li>
      <li>Leadership, management, and teamwork</li>
      <li>+ 6 additional domains of professional practice</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Do — Entrustable Professional Activities</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">8 EPAs</div>
      <p>Outlines the essential work tasks trainees need to be able to perform in the workplace.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Know — Knowledge Guides</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">35 knowledge guides</div>
      <p>18 Adult Medicine &nbsp;+&nbsp; 17 Paediatrics & Child Health</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Outlines the expected baseline knowledge of trainees.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
